      <div class="fw-list" id="fwList">

        <div class="fw" data-type="rule">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Execution Mode — Ciclo Completo Sem Parar</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-rule">RULE</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">NUNCA parar para perguntar. Executar ciclicamente, validar etapas enquanto avanca, entregar 100% completo.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>OUVIR o pedido completo</li>
              <li>RECALL contexto da memoria (segundo cerebro + MEMORY.md)</li>
              <li>CRIAR tasks para tudo que precisa ser feito</li>
              <li>EXECUTAR cada task em sequencia, marcando completed</li>
              <li>VALIDAR visualmente no browser (Puppeteer) em etapas criticas</li>
              <li>SE falta info que NAO pode ser inferida, perguntar. Senao, inferir e executar</li>
              <li>NUNCA entregar parcial com pergunta. Entregar TUDO</li>
              <li>SALVAR na memoria o que foi feito e decisoes tomadas</li>
              <li>COMMIT e PUSH no final</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">execution</span><span class="fw-tag">autonomous</span><span class="fw-tag">workflow</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: global · Trigger: TODA sessao, TODA tarefa</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="checklist">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Admin Panel Review (Ive + Nielsen)</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-checklist">CHECKLIST</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Framework para avaliar qualquer area admin como Jony Ive + Jakob Nielsen. 15 itens obrigatorios.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>VISIBILIDADE: Cada tab mostra status do sistema em tempo real?</li>
              <li>DRILL-DOWN: Todo card resumo tem link para detalhe? Zero dead-ends?</li>
              <li>CONSISTENCIA: Mesmo padrao visual em todas as tabs?</li>
              <li>SILENCIO VISUAL: Remover ate nao ter mais o que remover. Cada pixel tem proposito?</li>
              <li>HIERARQUIA: Stats em cima, detalhes no meio, drill-down embaixo?</li>
              <li>DARK MODE: #0A0A0A, cards #1C1C1E, borders 0.04, accent #D70030?</li>
              <li>NAVEGACAO IDA: SPA tabs linkam para TODAS sub-pages?</li>
              <li>NAVEGACAO VOLTA: Sub-pages sidebar preserva hash state?</li>
              <li>BREADCRUMB: Sub-pages mostram caminho Admin > Secao > Detalhe?</li>
              <li>TABELA CLICAVEL: Toda row leva ao detalhe? cursor:pointer?</li>
              <li>SIDEBAR COMPLETA: 10 tabs + utilidades + user info?</li>
              <li>MOBILE: Nao quebra em tablet</li>
              <li>ESCALA: Dados mockados refletem cenario real?</li>
              <li>ADVERSIDADE: Health mostra status degradado quando servico cai?</li>
              <li>COMPLIANCE: LGPD, audit logs, kill switches acessiveis?</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">admin</span><span class="fw-tag">review</span><span class="fw-tag">ive</span><span class="fw-tag">nielsen</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-prototype · Trigger: Criar/revisar area admin</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="rule">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Trillion-Dollar Scale Lens</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-rule">RULE</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Pensar como plataforma com milhoes de usuarios. Escala, efeito de rede, custo marginal zero.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>ESCALA: Funciona com 1 e com 100.000 tenants?</li>
              <li>MULTI-TENANT: Isolamento total, zero data leakage</li>
              <li>ADVERSIDADE: O que acontece se X falha? Status visual?</li>
              <li>MONETIZACAO: 7 camadas visiveis (RONIN→BAKUFU + extras)</li>
              <li>EFEITO DE REDE: Cada tenant melhora o produto?</li>
              <li>FLYWHEEL: Mais tenants > melhor IA > mais valor > mais tenants</li>
              <li>VERTICAL INTEGRATION: Agente controla toda a cadeia</li>
              <li>CUSTO MARGINAL ZERO: +1 tenant nao custa mais</li>
              <li>LOCK-IN POSITIVO: Quanto mais usa, mais dificil sair</li>
              <li>COMPLIANCE BY DESIGN: LGPD e auditoria sao features, nao afterthought</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">scale</span><span class="fw-tag">platform</span><span class="fw-tag">trillion</span><span class="fw-tag">strategy</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-assistant · Trigger: Criar qualquer feature</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="rule">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">AI-First Business Rules — Resultado > Solucao</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-rule">RULE</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Tendencia e a ENTREGA DO RESULTADO, nao a solucao agentica. O dono quer trabalho feito.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>RESULTADO PRIMEIRO: O que o dono recebe de valor?</li>
              <li>INVISIBILIDADE: Melhor agente e o que voce esquece que existe</li>
              <li>PROGRESSIVE DISCLOSURE: Resultado resumido, detalhe so se quiser</li>
              <li>CONFIANCA PROGRESSIVA: Mes 1 aprova tudo, mes 12 agente age sozinho</li>
              <li>METRICA: Nao e acoes feitas, e dinheiro/tempo economizado</li>
              <li>ROI VISIVEL: Extrato bancario de lucro, nao metricas tecnicas</li>
              <li>TRABALHO > FERRAMENTA: Mostrar resultado, nao processo</li>
              <li>HUMAN-IN-THE-LOOP MINIMO: Aprovacao so para irreversiveis</li>
              <li>FEEDBACK LOOP: Dono corrige, agente aprende. Nunca 2x</li>
              <li>COMPETIDOR: Nao e outro SaaS, e o funcionario. 10x mais barato, 3x mais rapido</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">ai-first</span><span class="fw-tag">business-rules</span><span class="fw-tag">resultado</span><span class="fw-tag">calm-tech</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-assistant · Trigger: Avaliar dashboards e chat</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="checklist">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Adversity & Risk Scenarios</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-checklist">CHECKLIST</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">14 cenarios de falha e risco para plataforma com milhares de clientes pagando.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>LLM PROVIDER CAI: Fallback automatico? Health mostra degraded?</li>
              <li>TENANT ABUSA: Rate limiting? Throttle automatico?</li>
              <li>AGENTE ALUCINA: Kill switch? Audit log?</li>
              <li>DADOS VAZAM: Isolamento multi-tenant verificado?</li>
              <li>PICO DE CARGA: Auto-scaling? Workers suficientes?</li>
              <li>CHURN EM MASSA: Early warning (usage drop)?</li>
              <li>COMPLIANCE BREACH: Export em 48h funciona?</li>
              <li>DEPLOY QUEBRA: Rollback 1 clique? Staging testado?</li>
              <li>MEMORIA CORROMPIDA: Dream engine consolida? Admin inspeciona brain?</li>
              <li>DONO SOME: Agentes pausam auto? Cobranca para?</li>
              <li>AGENTE CARO: Billing mostra breakdown por cargo?</li>
              <li>BRUTE FORCE: 2FA obrigatorio? Rate limit auth?</li>
              <li>ESCALA EQUIPE: 4→40 agentes escala visualmente?</li>
              <li>DOWNTIME: Status page? Comunicacao auto para tenants?</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">risk</span><span class="fw-tag">adversity</span><span class="fw-tag">resilience</span><span class="fw-tag">security</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-assistant · Trigger: Admin, health, billing, compliance</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="checklist">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Visual Navigation Review — Browser Flow</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-checklist">CHECKLIST</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Navegar todos os fluxos ponta a ponta no browser real antes de declarar pronto.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>ABRIR no Puppeteer com cache-bust</li>
              <li>FLUXO PJ: Landing→Signup→Verify→Plans→Checkout→Onboarding→Dashboard→Chat→Approvals→Team→Settings</li>
              <li>FLUXO PF: Landing→Signup→Verify→Onboarding→Areas→Mentor→Chat→Spirit</li>
              <li>FLUXO ADMIN: Overview→cada tab(10)→drill-down sub-pages(16)→volta via sidebar</li>
              <li>GUARD: Auth SEM nav. Landing SEM nav. Admin SEM nav light</li>
              <li>DEAD-END: Toda pagina tem saida</li>
              <li>LINK: Zero href=# exceto acoes inline</li>
              <li>SCREENSHOT de cada etapa critica</li>
              <li>SO declarar pronto apos TODAS evidencias visuais</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">qa</span><span class="fw-tag">navigation</span><span class="fw-tag">browser</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-prototype · Trigger: Mudanca em nav ou estrutura</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="template">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Screen Creation — Master Prompt</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-template">TEMPLATE</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Template completo para criar qualquer tela do zero com todo contexto.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>PROJETO: SaaS samurais IA. Repo ktanadev/ktana-prototype. 170+ HTMLs</li>
              <li>ESTRUTURA: /tenant/ PJ, /pf/ PF, /admin/ backoffice. shared.css + shared-nav.js</li>
              <li>CORES: #F5F5F7 light, #0A0A0A dark, #D70030 accent, cards #FFF r20</li>
              <li>FONTS: Inter (UI), Satoshi (body), Zen Dots (brand). Min 11px. Touch 44px</li>
              <li>AVATARES: Circulo + inicial. NUNCA imagens. CEO = #D70030</li>
              <li>ICONES: SVG inline 1.5 currentColor 24x24. NUNCA emojis/fontawesome</li>
              <li>ANIMACOES: fadeIn 0.4s, stagger delay, hover translateY(-1px), spring ease</li>
              <li>FILOSOFIA: Ive + Jobs + Calm Tech + Nielsen. Silencio = confianca</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">template</span><span class="fw-tag">creation</span><span class="fw-tag">design-system</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-prototype · Trigger: Criar nova tela HTML</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="pattern">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">SUPER CEREBRO — Metamodelo Neural</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-pattern">PATTERN</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Arquitetura cognitiva que orquestra todos os outros frameworks. O cerebro que pensa sobre como pensar.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>Knowledge Graph: entidades, relacoes, observations (quem existe e como conecta)</li>
              <li>Semantic Memory: facts, preferences (fatos sobre o mundo)</li>
              <li>Episodic Memory: episodes, sessions, decisions (o que aconteceu)</li>
              <li>Procedural Memory: procedures (como fazer — frameworks, regras, runbooks)</li>
              <li>Working Memory: working_items (estado atual, tarefas ativas)</li>
              <li>Dream Engine: consolida, merge, prune, archive (4 fases)</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">neural</span><span class="fw-tag">metamodel</span><span class="fw-tag">cognition</span><span class="fw-tag">memory</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-assistant · Trigger: Toda decisao arquitetural</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="pattern">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">KATANA SHIELD — Defesa Adversarial</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-pattern">PATTERN</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Mente criminal suprema de defesa. 3 sub-frameworks de seguranca ofensiva e defensiva.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>Adversarial Trinity: 3 vetores de ataque simulados constantemente</li>
              <li>Red Team Agent (Ronin): Hacker etico autonomo testando a propria plataforma</li>
              <li>Security Architecture: Infra hardening, encryption, auth, audit</li>
              <li>Kill Switches: Capacidade de desligar qualquer agente em 1 clique</li>
              <li>Constitution: 24 regras inviolaveis que nenhum agente pode quebrar</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">security</span><span class="fw-tag">red-team</span><span class="fw-tag">adversarial</span><span class="fw-tag">defense</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-assistant · Trigger: Review de seguranca</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="pattern">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Strategic Trinity — Musk + Jobs + Gates</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-pattern">PATTERN</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Conselho visionario. Cada decisao estrategica passa pelo filtro dos 3 mestres de escala.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>MUSK: 10x thinking, vertical integration, flywheel, first principles</li>
              <li>JOBS: Simplicidade radical, design como estrategia, experiencia > feature</li>
              <li>GATES: Platform play, developer ecosystem, enterprise lock-in, standards</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">strategy</span><span class="fw-tag">council</span><span class="fw-tag">vision</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: ktana-assistant · Trigger: Decisoes estrategicas de produto</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="checklist">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">22 Frameworks — Aplicar em cada tela</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-checklist">CHECKLIST</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">6 blocos de frameworks aplicados em toda tela criada.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>MESTRES (6): Filtros Ive, Nielsen, Jobs, Musk, Wozniak, Senna</li>
              <li>HCI (6): Calm Tech, Ambient Intelligence, ACID, Invisible Interface, Progressive Trust, DxD</li>
              <li>INTELIGENCIA (3): Simbiose Cognitiva, Metacognicao, Collective Intelligence</li>
              <li>NEGOCIO (3): Semantica do Produto, 7 Camadas Rentabilizacao, Prevencao Legal</li>
              <li>SEGURANCA (3): Adversarial Trinity, Constitution, Kill Switches</li>
              <li>VALIDACAO (1): Stress Test Atemporalidade — funciona em 2026 e em 2100</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">ktana</span><span class="fw-tag">design</span><span class="fw-tag">ux</span><span class="fw-tag">complete</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: shared · Trigger: Toda tela criada ou revisada</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="runbook">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Deploy Memory API</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-runbook">RUNBOOK</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Passos para deploy seguro da Memory API no VPS 960192.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>SSH para VPS 960192 (82.29.62.106)</li>
              <li>cd /opt/claude-memory && git pull</li>
              <li>docker compose build && docker compose up -d</li>
              <li>Verificar health: curl localhost:8000/api/v1/stats</li>
              <li>Verificar logs: docker logs claude-memory-api --tail 50</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">deploy</span><span class="fw-tag">memory</span><span class="fw-tag">docker</span><span class="fw-tag">vps</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: shared · Trigger: Atualizar API de memoria</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fw" data-type="runbook">
          <div class="fw-head" onclick="toggleFw(this)">
            <svg class="fw-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
            <p class="fw-name">Infra Migration — Hostinger → AWS</p>
            <span class="fw-type t-runbook">RUNBOOK</span>
            <div class="fw-toggle" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); this.classList.toggle('on')"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fw-body">
            <p class="fw-desc">Caminho de migracao sem trauma. Fases, rollback, zero downtime.</p>
            <ol class="fw-steps">
              <li>Fase 1: MVP em Hostinger VPS (atual)</li>
              <li>Fase 2: Docker Compose com Traefik (pronto)</li>
              <li>Fase 3: AWS ECS ou EKS quando > 100 tenants pagantes</li>
              <li>Fase 4: Multi-region quando > 1000 tenants</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="fw-tags-row"><span class="fw-tag">infra</span><span class="fw-tag">migration</span><span class="fw-tag">aws</span></div>
            <p class="fw-scope">Scope: shared · Trigger: Decisao de infra</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Clock
    setInterval(() => {
      document.getElementById('clock').textContent = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('pt-BR', { hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit', second:'2-digit' });
    }, 1000);
    document.getElementById('clock').textContent = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('pt-BR', { hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit', second:'2-digit' });

    // Toggle framework expand
    function toggleFw(head) {
      head.closest('.fw').classList.toggle('open');
    }

    // Filter frameworks
    function filterFw(type) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      event.target.classList.add('active');
      document.querySelectorAll('.fw').forEach(fw => {
        if (type === 'all' || fw.dataset.type === type) {
          fw.style.display = '';
        } else {
          fw.style.display = 'none';
        }
      });
    }

    // Agent Drawer
    const agents = {
      akira: { name:'Akira', role:'CEO', model:'Sonnet 4.6', fallback:'Haiku 4.5', temp:'0.3', tokens:'50.000', cost:'R$420', conns:'Gmail, WhatsApp, ClickUp', conf:'91%', skills:['Consolidar briefing diario','Delegar tasks para equipe','Escalar decisoes pro Shogun','Gerar relatorio semanal','Aprovar gastos < R$500'], refs:['Steve Jobs','Elon Musk','Ray Dalio'], rules:['Nunca enviar email externo sem aprovacao','Sempre incluir ROI estimado','Check-in diario 08:00 WhatsApp'] },
      yuki: { name:'Yuki', role:'Controller', model:'Sonnet 4.6', fallback:'Haiku 4.5', temp:'0.2', tokens:'30.000', cost:'R$280', conns:'Gmail, Bradesco API, Planilhas', conf:'94%', skills:['Conciliar pagamentos','Gerar DRE mensal','Fluxo de caixa semanal','Alerta de inadimplencia','Relatorio fiscal'], refs:['Warren Buffett','Ramit Sethi'], rules:['Nunca aprovar pagamento > R$5000','Sempre conferir com extrato bancario','Enviar DRE ate dia 5'] },
      hana: { name:'Hana', role:'Secretaria Executiva', model:'Haiku 4.5', fallback:'Haiku 4.5', temp:'0.1', tokens:'20.000', cost:'R$190', conns:'Gmail, Calendar, WhatsApp', conf:'96%', skills:['Filtrar emails','Agendar reunioes','Notificar via WhatsApp','Organizar documentos','Triage de urgencia'], refs:['Marie Kondo','Tim Ferriss'], rules:['Nunca agendar antes das 09:00','Prioridade para reunioes com cliente','Confirmar com Julio antes de cancelar'] },
      haruki: { name:'Haruki', role:'Gestor de Projetos', model:'Sonnet 4.6', fallback:'Haiku 4.5', temp:'0.3', tokens:'40.000', cost:'R$340', conns:'ClickUp, GitHub, Slack', conf:'89%', skills:['Sprint planning','Task decomposition','Dependency mapping','Weekly review','Escalar bloqueios'], refs:['David Allen','Cal Newport','Basecamp'], rules:['Sprint max 2 semanas','Escalar bloqueio em 24h','Daily standup 09:30'] },
      kaito: { name:'Kaito', role:'Solutions Builder', model:'Opus 4.6', fallback:'Sonnet 4.6', temp:'0.4', tokens:'60.000', cost:'R$520', conns:'GitHub, Vercel, APIs', conf:'87%', skills:['Criar modulos marketplace','Integrar APIs externas','Prototipar solucoes','Documentar specs','Testar end-to-end'], refs:['Linus Torvalds','DHH'], rules:['Code review obrigatorio','Zero deploy sem teste','Documentar toda API'] },
      yumi: { name:'Yumi', role:'Mentora PF', model:'Sonnet 4.6', fallback:'Haiku 4.5', temp:'0.5', tokens:'25.000', cost:'R$230', conns:'WhatsApp, Calendar, Health', conf:'92%', skills:['Onboarding pessoal','Configurar mentores','Plano de vida','Check-in semanal','Radar espiritual'], refs:['Brene Brown','James Clear','Viktor Frankl'], rules:['Tom empatico sempre','Nunca julgar escolhas','Respeitar ritmo do usuario'] }
    };

    function openAgent(id) {
      const a = agents[id];
      if (!a) return;
      document.getElementById('drawerTitle').textContent = a.name + ' — ' + a.role;
      document.getElementById('feedSection').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('agentDrawer').style.display = '';
      // Update config tab
      const configRows = document.querySelector('#tab-config .config-rows');
      configRows.innerHTML = [
        ['Modelo LLM', a.model], ['Fallback', a.fallback], ['Temperatura', a.temp],
        ['Max tokens/dia', a.tokens], ['Custo/mes', a.cost], ['Conexoes', a.conns],
        ['Nivel confianca', a.conf]
      ].map(([l,v]) => `<div class="config-row"><span class="config-label">${l}</span><span class="config-val"${v.includes('%')?` style="color:#30D158"`:``}>${v}</span></div>`).join('');
      // Update training tab
      const skillsEl = document.querySelector('#tab-train .train-skills');
      skillsEl.innerHTML = a.skills.map(s => `<div class="train-skill"><span class="train-skill-name">${s}</span><div class="fw-toggle on" onclick="this.classList.toggle('on')"></div></div>`).join('');
      const refsEl = document.querySelector('#tab-train .train-refs');
      refsEl.innerHTML = a.refs.map(r => `<span class="train-ref">${r}</span>`).join('') + '<span class="train-ref" style="color:#D70030;background:rgba(215,0,48,0.08);">+ Adicionar</span>';
      const rulesEl = document.querySelector('#tab-train .train-rules');
      rulesEl.innerHTML = a.rules.map(r => `<p class="train-rule">${r}</p>`).join('');
      // Reset to chat tab
      switchDrawerTab(document.querySelector('.drawer-tab'), 'chat');
      // Highlight active agent
      document.querySelectorAll('.agent-mini').forEach(m => m.classList.remove('active'));
      event.currentTarget.classList.add('active');
    }

    function closeAgent() {
      document.getElementById('agentDrawer').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('feedSection').style.display = '';
    }

    function switchDrawerTab(btn, tabId) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.drawer-tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      ['chat','train','config'].forEach(id => {
        document.getElementById('tab-' + id).style.display = id === tabId ? '' : 'none';
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
